subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Coaches and Managers
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Ann Grossman Wunderlich, who reached the fourth round of the United States Open in 1994, is coaching the junior Francesca Di Lorenzo, who reached the semifinals of this year’s girls’ tournament.
